{
  "texts": [
    "This activity enables students to practice qualitative techniques, improve their interview skills, and analyze content.",
    "By preparing interview scripts and discussion topics, students engage with ChatGPT, which acts as a participant, providing responses from various perspectives.",
    "These simulated interactions allow students to identify patterns and refine their qualitative data collection techniques through analysis of the generated responses.",
    "V. DISCUSSIONThe developed study confirms and expands on the findings of previous studies on the integration of ChatGPT in education, revealing both benefits and challenges.",
    "According to Watrianthos et al."
  ]
}